OL,3,CSenior doctor says wearing masks on
OL,4,Cwards 'vital' as flu cases surge
OL,6,FA doctor at a Surrey hospital says
OL,7,Fmask wearing on wards is 'vital' to
OL,8,Fprotect patients and staff as flu
OL,9,Fcases continue to surge.
OL,11,FFrimley Park Hospital near Camberley
OL,12,Fhas introduced the measure as NHS
OL,13,Ffigures show that this mutation of flu
OL,14,Fis responsible for 2600 hospital
OL,15,Fadmissions a day across the country,
OL,16,Fup from 1800 last year.
OL,18,FNationally, the number of flu patients
OL,19,Fhas spiked by 55% in a week, as
OL,20,FDecember brings a surge of "super flu".
