OL,3,CSenior doctor says wearing masks on
OL,4,Cwards 'vital' as flu cases surge
OL,6,FDr Gareth Roberts, who's a respiratory
OL,7,Fconsultant, said: "We know that mask
OL,8,Fwearing...certainly goes a long way to
OL,9,Ftry to help reduce transmission
OL,10,Fbetween individuals.
OL,12,F"It is something that we have
OL,13,Fobviously experience of when it comes
OL,14,Fpreviously to viral infections and we
OL,15,Fhave a huge amount of support from all
OL,16,Fof our teams to make sure that we're
OL,17,Fdoing what we can to really ensure
OL,18,Fwe're providing ongoing patient care."
