OL,3,CSenior doctor says wearing masks on
OL,4,Cwards 'vital' as flu cases surge
OL,6,FDr Roberts continued: "We're certainly
OL,7,Fvery concerned about it (flu cases) at
OL,8,Fthe moment. We've seen numbers
OL,9,Fincreasing at an earlier time than
OL,10,Fwhat we'd normally expect.
OL,12,F"And certainly over the last few
OL,13,Fweeks, we've seen those numbers
OL,14,Fdoubling on a week by week basis."
OL,16,FAsked about the impact of a potential
OL,17,Fstrike by resident doctors next week,
OL,18,FDr Roberts said: "That is something
OL,19,Fwe've already been prepared for.
