OL,3,CSenior doctor says wearing masks on
OL,4,Cwards 'vital' as flu cases surge
OL,6,F"We've made arrangements to ensure
OL,7,Fthat we have adequate cover."
OL,9,F"Ultimately it will create an
OL,10,Fadditional amount of pressure, (but)
OL,11,Fit's something that we are prepared
OL,12,Ffor at the moment and doing everything
OL,13,Fwe can to ensure continued patient
OL,14,Fcare without any interruption as far
OL,15,Fas possible."
OL,17,FNurse Andreia Simoes was clear that
OL,18,Fgetting a vaccine is vital to helping
OL,19,Fthe fight against flu.
