OL,3,CSenior doctor says wearing masks on
OL,4,Cwards 'vital' as flu cases surge
OL,6,FShe said: "Get a vaccine if you
OL,7,Fhaven't had it. Make sure if you
OL,8,Fdevelop any symptoms that you isolate
OL,9,Fyourself as much as you can and
OL,10,Frestrict yourself from contact with
OL,11,Fimmunosuppressed colleagues or family
OL,12,Fmembers."
OL,14,FThe UK Health Security Agency says
OL,15,Fearly data shows this year's vaccine
OL,16,Fis offering good protection despite
OL,17,Fthe new strain now driving most cases.
